  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t1.肖像<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODUxMzdmNTc5Mzc2NDM4ZjRkOTVhLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/85137f579376438f4d95a.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/85137f579376438f4d95a.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/85137f579376438f4d95a.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n2.1998年，王冶坪陪江泽民访日，旁为日本皇后美智子。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGZjODUxOWNlNWRmMTdjNWFlN2UyLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0fc8519ce5df17c5ae7e2.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0fc8519ce5df17c5ae7e2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0fc8519ce5df17c5ae7e2.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n3.2001年，王冶坪与江泽民在大溪地，下楼梯时她自然地挽着他的臂膀。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGQwZDkzMTcxNWFiYmQ1MDgyZGFkLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4d0d931715abbd5082dad.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4d0d931715abbd5082dad.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4d0d931715abbd5082dad.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n4.1997年，江泽民偕妻访美，位于维吉尼亚州殖民时期的帽子。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMDNkNjYyZGIwNjEzZWUwYWRlYWFjLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/03d662db0613ee0adeaac.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/03d662db0613ee0adeaac.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/03d662db0613ee0adeaac.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n5.2001年，王冶坪伴夫访俄罗斯，在克林姆林宫与当时普丁的夫人共餐。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDk0NTJiY2MwNDcwZWU1YmNkZDg4LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d9452bcc0470ee5bcdd88.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d9452bcc0470ee5bcdd88.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d9452bcc0470ee5bcdd88.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n6.1997年摄于北京人民大会堂。 王冶坪常被拍到走在江泽民身后，相距2、3步。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOGQ4MTMzZGEwOTFmNWUxMjhlZDAxLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8d8133da091f5e128ed01.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8d8133da091f5e128ed01.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8d8133da091f5e128ed01.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n7.2002年，江泽民与夫人王冶坪访港<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYmQ2ZDBmMTRjNjQ5YmRiMTNlNDQ5LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bd6d0f14c649bdb13e449.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bd6d0f14c649bdb13e449.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bd6d0f14c649bdb13e449.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n8.1999，江泽民夫妇访法国里昂，他拉着王冶坪的手。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMDZiYTI3YzJiODljYjhkY2QyNDYzLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/06ba27c2b89cb8dcd2463.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/06ba27c2b89cb8dcd2463.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/06ba27c2b89cb8dcd2463.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n9.2001年，江泽民夫妻访越南河内，他让她扶着下飞机。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTEzYjlhNGViYjZlMDJjMGY1ZTQyLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a13b9a4ebb6e02c0f5e42.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a13b9a4ebb6e02c0f5e42.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a13b9a4ebb6e02c0f5e42.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n10.1997年，王冶坪伴夫访美，时任美国总统柯林顿、第一夫人希拉蕊相迎。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMjEzNDdiZTA0ZGFjZjZjNmNkNTA2LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/21347be04dacf6c6cd506.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/21347be04dacf6c6cd506.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/21347be04dacf6c6cd506.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> <br/>\r\n11.2002年，美国总统布希（左二）与第一夫人萝拉（右），邀请江泽民夫妇前往德州其私人农场参加家宴。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjE0NDUzYzIzZjRjZGVlZmI4ZWVjLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b14453c23f4cdeefb8eec.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b14453c23f4cdeefb8eec.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b14453c23f4cdeefb8eec.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n12.江泽民与王冶坪1992年在北京玉泉山合影<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzc5NDFjMTE4OTRiYTliM2VmYWJlLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/77941c11894ba9b3efabe.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/77941c11894ba9b3efabe.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/77941c11894ba9b3efabe.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n13.王冶坪与董建华夫人董赵洪娉亲切交谈。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDgyMGY5YzM4YjMxZTMwNDFkMTA5LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d820f9c38b31e3041d109.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d820f9c38b31e3041d109.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d820f9c38b31e3041d109.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a>  <br/>\r\n14.1998年11月28日，江同志和夫人王冶坪乘坐新干线赴仙台，晚上抵达仙台后出席了宫城县知事浅野史郎举行的欢迎晚宴。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMzExYThlNDViMmE3Y2JhMWNmYzZkLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/311a8e45b2a7cba1cfc6d.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/311a8e45b2a7cba1cfc6d.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/311a8e45b2a7cba1cfc6d.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n15.江泽民王冶坪夫妇与学生们合影<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTA3MGZlNjIwZTMyNWQwZTU3ZjA4LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5070fe620e325d0e57f08.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5070fe620e325d0e57f08.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5070fe620e325d0e57f08.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n16.江泽民携王冶坪去地方视察时与宾馆服务人员合影<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvM2E2NWQ1Y2RiNzllZTVmZjY3YTc5LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3a65d5cdb79ee5ff67a79.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3a65d5cdb79ee5ff67a79.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3a65d5cdb79ee5ff67a79.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n17.江泽民离港，时任行政长官董建华与他握手道别，王冶坪默默地站在丈夫身后。 <a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTRhNTBjMDZhODgwY2NhMTgyOGMwLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a4a50c06a880cca1828c0.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a4a50c06a880cca1828c0.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a4a50c06a880cca1828c0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n18.王冶坪陪同国家主席江泽民外访<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZjA4N2NlZjc2MTRmMTk2MzExNDQ3LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f087cef7614f196311447.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f087cef7614f196311447.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f087cef7614f196311447.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n19.1999年访问法国期间，会见希拉克总统夫<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGYyYzIwOTUzMzhkNzk5ZTVjNWI3LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4f2c2095338d799e5c5b7.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4f2c2095338d799e5c5b7.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4f2c2095338d799e5c5b7.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n20.江泽民搀扶王冶坪下飞机<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMTJkOWI0YzZjYzMzY2Q4ZjU4NDA3LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/12d9b4c6cc33cd8f58407.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/12d9b4c6cc33cd8f58407.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/12d9b4c6cc33cd8f58407.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n21.2001年，王冶坪伴江泽民出访阿根廷，下机时王冶坪挽着江泽民的手<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTE0Nzk0OTFjMTJhNWNjZTA0ZmMzLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/51479491c12a5cce04fc3.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/51479491c12a5cce04fc3.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/51479491c12a5cce04fc3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n22.江泽民全家福：（左起）江绵恒、王冶坪、江泽民、江绵康。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZjI1MTNkYzY3YjIwYWQyMDMwMTY1LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f2513dc67b20ad2030165.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f2513dc67b20ad2030165.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f2513dc67b20ad2030165.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n23.江泽民2022年生日合影<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYWMzNTJkYTY0ZGI4ZWFmYmMzNTI0LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ac352da64db8eafbc3524.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ac352da64db8eafbc3524.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ac352da64db8eafbc3524.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n24.江泽民与孙儿合照。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMzQwNzVlMjY4ZDY5YjMzOGEzYzgyLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/34075e268d69b338a3c82.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/34075e268d69b338a3c82.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/34075e268d69b338a3c82.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n25.王冶坪肖像<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvM2E4ODNhZmEzZGRkMWRiNTZkYjNhLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3a883afa3ddd1db56db3a.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3a883afa3ddd1db56db3a.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3a883afa3ddd1db56db3a.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n26.1998年6月，江泽民王冶坪夫妇与来访的克林顿总统夫妇互致问候。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYmM4NzVlZjdkZWY3M2RkMWI2NjcyLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bc875ef7def73dd1b6672.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bc875ef7def73dd1b6672.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bc875ef7def73dd1b6672.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n27.江泽民和王冶坪游览漓江<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOWM1OTI2NWIyN2I4YTczYzRmYjg1LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9c59265b27b8a73c4fb85.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9c59265b27b8a73c4fb85.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9c59265b27b8a73c4fb85.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n28.江泽民与胡锦涛、朱镕基交谈，王冶坪与朱镕基握手<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGQwMmQ3MWYxMTQ3MjMyNjM4MDBjLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dd02d71f114723263800c.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dd02d71f114723263800c.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dd02d71f114723263800c.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n29.1999年10月24日江泽民与法国总统希拉克夫人跳舞。（AFP）<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTMxNDgyMDFkNzFjNjNkZTJmMjE3LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e3148201d71c63de2f217.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e3148201d71c63de2f217.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e3148201d71c63de2f217.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n30.王冶坪紧跟江泽民<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvY2M3NGIxZWQ3OWVlMjcyNGYyYTRjLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cc74b1ed79ee2724f2a4c.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cc74b1ed79ee2724f2a4c.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cc74b1ed79ee2724f2a4c.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n30.？<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMjU3MWYyY2VmYjRhMThlZDZiNDc1LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2571f2cefb4a18ed6b475.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2571f2cefb4a18ed6b475.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2571f2cefb4a18ed6b475.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n31.<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMWIxYjk2MTU1NTU0YzFhNDc0M2FiLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1b1b96155554c1a4743ab.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1b1b96155554c1a4743ab.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1b1b96155554c1a4743ab.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n32.<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOWU2YWIzMDFkMWMxOThjYTNmMDJlLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9e6ab301d1c198ca3f02e.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9e6ab301d1c198ca3f02e.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9e6ab301d1c198ca3f02e.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n33.2022年12月11日将江泽民骨灰撒入江海<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzg2ZTQ5ZDMwZjQwMThmYWZhZjAyLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/786e49d30f4018fafaf02.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/786e49d30f4018fafaf02.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/786e49d30f4018fafaf02.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n34.2022年12月5日江泽民送别仪式上坐在轮椅上的王冶坪<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODQ0OTM0YWYwYzBiMGNhMmRiNTMyLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/844934af0c0b0ca2db532.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/844934af0c0b0ca2db532.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/844934af0c0b0ca2db532.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n35.习近平等慰问江泽民亲属，习近平向王冶坪一鞠躬后，王冶坪双手合十<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNmNiMWYxNzkxNjhjNDE1ZWJiMmFhLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6cb1f179168c415ebb2aa.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6cb1f179168c415ebb2aa.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6cb1f179168c415ebb2aa.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n36.胡锦涛向王冶坪握手、双手合十<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMDhjZGFjOTI5YzZjZjY3OTdlNTExLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/08cdac929c6cf6797e511.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/08cdac929c6cf6797e511.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/08cdac929c6cf6797e511.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n37.2022年11月30日江泽民逝世，12月1日遗体由专机送抵北京，94岁遗孀王冶坪在江泽民透明棺前<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNDMwYmFkY2U4MGM2MTc4YTdmYzA5LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/430badce80c6178a7fc09.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/430badce80c6178a7fc09.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/430badce80c6178a7fc09.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n38.2022年12月6日上午10时江泽民追悼大会上的王冶坪<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZjgyY2Q0OWQ4ODEwYTdmM2FmNDQxLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f82cd49d8810a7f3af441.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f82cd49d8810a7f3af441.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f82cd49d8810a7f3af441.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n39.1961年8月，时年33岁的王冶坪<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMjU2OGY5M2MyMjVlN2ZmYmMxMTlmLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2568f93c225e7ffbc119f.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2568f93c225e7ffbc119f.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2568f93c225e7ffbc119f.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n40.爱丁堡公爵菲利普亲王、王冶坪、江泽民、伊丽莎白二世合影<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYzBlY2JhMzk5ZTE4OTdkYTA5YTE4LmpwZz93aWR0aD02MjAmaGVpZ2h0PTQwNg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c0ecba399e1897da09a18.jpg?width=620&amp;height=406\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c0ecba399e1897da09a18.jpg?width=620&amp;height=406\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c0ecba399e1897da09a18.jpg?width=620&amp;height=406\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n41.<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGU0NTU4ZmEyNzIxM2RjOTg1NDlhLmpwZz93aWR0aD02NDAmaGVpZ2h0PTQzNQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4e4558fa27213dc98549a.jpg?width=640&amp;height=435\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4e4558fa27213dc98549a.jpg?width=640&amp;height=435\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4e4558fa27213dc98549a.jpg?width=640&amp;height=435\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n42.<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvN2FhYjZhYWEzODM5YzIyYzVlZmJjLmpwZz93aWR0aD02NDAmaGVpZ2h0PTM2MA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7aab6aaa3839c22c5efbc.jpg?width=640&amp;height=360\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7aab6aaa3839c22c5efbc.jpg?width=640&amp;height=360\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7aab6aaa3839c22c5efbc.jpg?width=640&amp;height=360\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
